HEADWORD: Equipendency
<hw>E`qui*pend"en*cy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Equi-</ets> + <ets>pendency</ets>.]</ety> <def>The act or
condition of hanging in equipoise; not inclined or determined either
way.</def> <rj><au>South.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
